'''梅久戈耶/默主歌耶/梅杜高濟'''（'''{{lang-hr|Međugorje}}'''）是位於[[波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納|波士尼亞與赫塞哥維納]]南部的一個小城。梅久戈耶的人口是2306人<ref name="www.fzs.ba">[http://www.fzs.ba/PopisNaseljenaM.pdf FEDERAL OFFICE OF STATISTICS] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150513043659/http://www.fzs.ba/PopisNaseljenaM.pdf |date=2015-05-13 }}</ref>，大部分都是克羅埃西亞人。在1981年，有數人稱在梅久戈耶看到了[[聖母瑪利亞|聖母瑪利亞]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.medjugorje.ws/en/messages/docs-short-history/ |title=A short history of Our Lady's apparitions in Medjugorje |accessdate=2015-12-24 |archive-date=2015-12-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151222142236/http://www.medjugorje.ws/en/messages/docs-short-history/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.medjugorje.eu/messages All the alleged messages from the beginning in 1981 until today – on one page] {{Wayback|url=http://www.medjugorje.eu/messages |date=20160106020552 }}, message part of the book ''Messages and Teachings of Mary at Medjugorje'' by [[René_Laurentin|René Laurentin]] and René Lejeune, extended with the messages until this day from the website of the [http://www.medjugorje.hr Parish of Medjugorje] {{Wayback|url=http://www.medjugorje.hr/ |date=20150407123439 }} and other web sites related to Medjugorje.</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.medjugorje.com/medjugorje/medjugorje-visionaries/585-marija.html |title=Seer Marija Lunetti who reports to receive the twenty-fifth message |accessdate=2015-12-24 |archive-date=2016-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106020552/http://www.medjugorje.com/medjugorje/medjugorje-visionaries/585-marija.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.medjugorje.com/medjugorje/medjugorje-visionaries/583-mirjana.html |title=Seer Mirjana Soldo who reports to receive the message on the second of the month |accessdate=2015-12-24 |archive-date=2016-01-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160106020552/http://www.medjugorje.com/medjugorje/medjugorje-visionaries/583-mirjana.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然教廷未有承認梅久戈耶出現的是真正的聖母瑪利亞，但前往梅久戈耶朝聖的人絡繹不絕<ref>[http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/australian-dies-in-bosnia-bus-crash/2008/05/24/1211183195802.html Australian dies in Bosnia bus crash.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/australian-dies-in-bosnia-bus-crash/2008/05/24/1211183195802.html |date=20151018130640 }} ''Sydney Morning Herald. Retrieved 28 February 2010.</ref>。現在梅久戈耶已經成為天主教徒重要的朝聖地，是歐洲朝聖者數第三多的聖母顯現地，每年有超過100萬人來訪<ref>[http://www.romereports.com/palio/Visionaries-of-Medjugorje-may-appear-before-the-Vatican-english-2441.html RomeReports: Visionaries of Medjugorje may appear before the Vatican.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130505053250/http://www.romereports.com/palio/Visionaries-of-Medjugorje-may-appear-before-the-Vatican-english-2441.html |date=2013-05-05 }} ''Retrieved Feb 26 2011.''</ref>。

